				"description": "# DocuSign Clone API Testing\n\n## Setup\n\n1. Set environment variables:\n   - `base_url`: Your API base URL (e.g., http://localhost/api/v2.1)\n   - `access_token`: Will be auto-populated after login\n   - `account_id`: Will be auto-populated after account creation\n   - `envelope_id`: Will be auto-populated after envelope creation\n\n2. Run the \"Login\" request first to get your access token\n\n3. Create an account using \"Create Account\" to get your account_id\n\n4. All subsequent requests will use the bearer token automatically\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### 1. Authentication Flow\n- Register → Login → Get User → Logout\n\n### 2. Account Setup\n- Create Account → Get Account → Update Settings\n\n### 3. User Management\n- Create Users → Assign Permissions → Manage Profiles\n\n### 4. Envelope Workflow\n- Create Draft → Add Documents → Add Recipients → Send → Track\n\n### 5. Webhook Setup\n- Configure Connect → Test Delivery → Monitor Logs\n\n## All Modules (336 Endpoints)\n\nThis collection includes endpoints for:\n- ✅ Authentication (7)\n- ✅ Accounts (45)\n- ✅ Users (35)\n- ✅ Envelopes (29)\n- ✅ Billing (26)\n- ✅ Signatures (21)\n- ✅ Documents (18)\n- ✅ Connect/Webhooks (17)\n- ✅ Groups (16)\n- ✅ Brands (14)\n- ✅ Bulk Operations (13)\n- ✅ Workspaces (13)\n- ✅ Signing Groups (12)\n- ✅ Templates (11)\n- ✅ Recipients (10)\n- ✅ PowerForms (9)\n- ✅ Diagnostics (9)\n- ✅ Workflows (8)\n- ✅ Settings (6)\n- ✅ Tabs (6)\n- ✅ Chunked Uploads (6)\n- ✅ Envelope Downloads (5)\n- ✅ Folders (5)\n- ✅ Identity Verification (2)\n\n## Notes\n\n- All requests use bearer token authentication\n- Response times should be < 200ms for most endpoints\n- Test with different user roles for permission testing\n- Monitor logs in Diagnostics module\n"
